PROBLEM: I/P- N=7 , K=2         (Binary representation- 111)
         O/P- 3                 (Binary representation- 101)
         
         
         Explain:   111
                  & 101
                    101 is result
         
         
SOLUTION:

int TurnOffKthBit(int N){
  int a=1;
  a=~(a<<(k-1));
  return (N & a);
}
